name: Diana Dumitrescu
description: Theme: Casual Charm with Floral Whispers for a Relaxed, Rustic and Playful event. Think of a laid-back garden party, where fresh wildflowers like daisies and lavender are thoughtfully arranged in mason jars, scattered across rustic wooden tables. The flowers spill over in natural, unstructured arrangements, capturing the effortless charm of a countryside gathering. Neutral tones and soft textures create a calm ambiance.
